description: Northern California Bancorp, Inc. operates as the bank holding company for Monterey County Bank that provides various banking products and services in California. Its deposit products include checking and savings accounts, certificates of deposit, and individual retirement accounts. The company offers small business administration and commercial loans; merchant services; credit and debit cards; and internet banking services. Northern California Bancorp, Inc. was founded in 1977 and is based in Monterey, California.
